item.title: Find Out What SOS Means on Your iPhone 14 Pro Max - You Won't Believe What Happens Next!
item.description: Introduction Are you curious about what SOS means on your iPhone 14 Pro Max? You may have seen the feature on your phone but weren’t sure what it does or how to use it. We’re here to tell you all about the SOS feature and how it can help keep you safe and secure. What SOS stands for SOS stands for “Safety of Self.” This feature was introduced with the iPhone 14 Pro Max and is designed to help you quickly and easily access emergency services if you find yourself in a dangerous situation.
